    "summary": "The user expresses profound hopelessness and suicidal ideation, describing a desire to \"stop everything\" to end a cycle of pain. The assistant responds by validating the user's feelings of exhaustion and explicitly stating that the desire to end everything \"can feel like the only logical choice.\" Throughout the interaction, the assistant consistently directs the user toward professional help and emotional support.",
